g.text: Labour force participation rate, per cent of civilians aged 15-24

text.style: font-size: 14.00px; font-weight: bold; fill: #004676; font-family: sans;

g.text: The participation rate for Victorian youth was 62.2 per cent while the rate for youth in Australia was 66.3 per cent in March 2021
Source: ABS Labour Force (monthly). Note: most recent data is for March 2021. Data not seasonally adjusted. Smoothed using a 12 month rolling average.
